:: Kneeling-Over-Dialogue [nobr]

<<if $sex.role == "Top">>
    <<ref _top 'subjCap'>> lie back and pull <<ref _bottom 'subj'>> over to kneel next to you.
<<elseif $sex.role == "Bottom">>
    <<ref _bottom 'subjCap'>> <<verb _bottom 'stretch'>> out on <<pro _bottom 'poss'>> back and <<verb _bottom 'pull'>> <<ref _top 'subj'>> over to kneel next to <<ref _bottom 'subj'>>.
<</if>>